  "detailed_description": "Magic Farm 3: The Ice Danger is an adventure at your own pace. Take care of your farms and customize them as you see fit. Explore the magic world, solve quests, meet people and trade for the rare goods.\u200b<br />\r\n<br />\r\nWhat is waiting for you:<br />\r\n<br />\r\n- Meet with familiar old characters and make more new friends<br />\r\n<br />\r\n- Favorite gameplay with a lot of improvements<br />\r\n<br />\r\n- 4 new amazing locations<br />\r\n<br />\r\n- More than 100 quests<br />\r\n<br />\r\n- Think strategic \u2014 choose how to achieve goals<br />\r\n<br />\r\n- Leveling up main characters makes the gameplay progressively interesting. You can choose who you are: a brawler who fights with enemies or a gardener who forces everything to bloom around with a wave of the hand<br />\r\n<br />\r\n- Additional quests and free gameplay in open locations",
  "about_the_game": "Magic Farm 3: The Ice Danger is an adventure at your own pace. Take care of your farms and customize them as you see fit. Explore the magic world, solve quests, meet people and trade for the rare goods.\u200b<br />\r\n<br />\r\nWhat is waiting for you:<br />\r\n<br />\r\n- Meet with familiar old characters and make more new friends<br />\r\n<br />\r\n- Favorite gameplay with a lot of improvements<br />\r\n<br />\r\n- 4 new amazing locations<br />\r\n<br />\r\n- More than 100 quests<br />\r\n<br />\r\n- Think strategic \u2014 choose how to achieve goals<br />\r\n<br />\r\n- Leveling up main characters makes the gameplay progressively interesting. You can choose who you are: a brawler who fights with enemies or a gardener who forces everything to bloom around with a wave of the hand<br />\r\n<br />\r\n- Additional quests and free gameplay in open locations",
  "short_description": "&quot;Magic Farm 3: The Ice Danger&quot; is a farming simulator game, with a simple-RPG system and quests. This is a continuation of the Magic Farm series for PC and Mac. You'll play as an Iris, a girl with an ability to grow magical plants who need to take care of her new farms.",
